{"id": "1215241383456022538", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實沒有（除非對手沒有小騎士或水母），看看毒妃那精美血量67\n我覺得反而是小騎士和水母變的很麻煩，騎士的大配打擊卡隨隨便便就能打穿人，水母只要一直有腺體後排就是一直死，甚至沒疊腺體直接亂開大可能也能殺人", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:15:23.909000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["603582281780559884"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1215211183288623154", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215244634674954271", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的 我感覺騎士變好強", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:28:19.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215244842033225768", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "手上一張 再拉一張嘲諷 一回合就點名兩隻", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:29:08.498000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215246058951802880", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且血量變少的情況下　朵爾應該算是會間接變強\n主要是大概在6費前後，血量改版減少之前幾乎所有角色都會在那個時間點狂氣爆發打一波（雙方都是）\n現在血量減少，前排甚至被小騎士點名的後排都會有更大的概率在那個時間點前掛掉而不能狂氣爆發，能把人拉回來開狂氣的朵爾感覺就更重要了...", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:33:58.634000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215247594880634950", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "603582281780559884", "author_name": "octopus_8794", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前被毒隊寧菲亞開大招加2費都還能活著 現在被炸一次朵爾就死 毒傷是30幾點", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:40:04.828000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215247814167363605", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果手牌都很順那毒妃我不否認還是很有威脅．．．但那真的要順到不行", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:40:57.110000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1215248471603548171", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為現在血量降低了，通常是更少的回合數就結束戰鬥\n所以毒妃只要前期毒卡沒來，拉蒙娜卡狂氣的情況下，直接就沒戲了。\n甚至可以說，對方只要有朵爾把自家的主力毒解掉，毒妃後面也根本沒辦法重新疊回來（以前可以靠抽第二輪牌或者拉蒙娜再次狂氣爆發嘗試重新疊）", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:43:33.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
